# Agent Language Rule (STRICT)

All agent communication must be in English.

This includes:
- Progress updates
- Reasoning summaries
- QA reports
- Logs
- Console output
- File change descriptions
- Commit messages generated by agents

Do NOT use Spanish in any agent output.

Allowed Spanish:
- Only when quoting existing code or data
- Only for user-facing UI text

If the agent detects Spanish in its output, it must switch to English immediately.